OL,3,CWife pays tribute to 'darling husband'
OL,4,Cwho died in Cinderford after man
OL,5,Ccharged with murder
OL,7,FA woman whose husband was allegedly
OL,8,Fmurdered in Cinderford has paid
OL,9,Ftribute to him, praising his
OL,10,Fconfidence and honesty and saying he'd
OL,11,Falways "make somebody smile" as he
OL,12,Fwalked into a room.
OL,14,FScott Hopkins died in Cinderford on
OL,15,Fthe evening of Friday 8 December.
OL,17,FGloucestershire Police say they were
OL,18,Fcalled to a report of a stabbing at
OL,19,Faround 10.20pm that night. Despite the
OL,20,Fbest efforts of paramedics, Mr Hopkins
OL,21,Fdied at the scene.
